  "transcript": {
    "language": "en",
    "is_generated": false,
    "segments": [
      {
        "start": 0.2,
        "duration": 1.0,
        "text": "- [Instructor] Hi, a wordsmiths."
      },
      {
        "start": 1.2,
        "duration": 2.9,
        "text": "Let's break down some vocabulary words."
      },
      {
        "start": 4.0,
        "duration": 4.0,
        "text": "The words for this video\nare express and immerse."
      },
      {
        "start": 8.0,
        "duration": 2.5,
        "text": "Let's do definitions."
      },
      {
        "start": 10.6,
        "duration": 1.4,
        "text": "Express."
      },
      {
        "start": 12.0,
        "duration": 2.9,
        "text": "Express is a verb, means to communicate,"
      },
      {
        "start": 14.9,
        "duration": 2.1,
        "text": "to show what you think or feel."
      },
      {
        "start": 17.0,
        "duration": 2.4,
        "text": "There's also expression, which is a noun,"
      },
      {
        "start": 19.4,
        "duration": 4.0,
        "text": "means a common saying, or\nthe act of communicating"
      },
      {
        "start": 23.4,
        "duration": 1.5,
        "text": "or facial expression,"
      },
      {
        "start": 24.9,
        "duration": 2.1,
        "text": "like the delighted face I make"
      },
      {
        "start": 27.0,
        "duration": 1.6,
        "text": "when I learn a new word."
      },
      {
        "start": 28.6,
        "duration": 2.0,
        "text": "I have a delighted expression."
      },
      {
        "start": 30.6,
        "duration": 2.5,
        "text": "And immerse is also a verb."
      },
      {
        "start": 33.1,
        "duration": 1.6,
        "text": "It means to put something under water"
      },
      {
        "start": 34.7,
        "duration": 3.4,
        "text": "or to get deeply involved\nor interested in something."
      },
      {
        "start": 38.1,
        "duration": 2.8,
        "text": "There's also an adjectival\nform of immersive,"
      },
      {
        "start": 40.9,
        "duration": 1.9,
        "text": "which is immersive."
      },
      {
        "start": 42.8,
        "duration": 2.7,
        "text": "And this adjective means making someone"
      },
      {
        "start": 45.5,
        "duration": 2.0,
        "text": "feel like they're completely surrounded"
      },
      {
        "start": 47.5,
        "duration": 2.9,
        "text": "or involved in an experience."
      },
      {
        "start": 50.5,
        "duration": 1.5,
        "text": "Like virtual reality,"
      },
      {
        "start": 52.0,
        "duration": 1.3,
        "text": "where you put on the goggles"
      },
      {
        "start": 53.2,
        "duration": 2.0,
        "text": "and it feels like you're\nin the video game."
      },
      {
        "start": 55.3,
        "duration": 1.6,
        "text": "That's immersive."
      },
      {
        "start": 56.9,
        "duration": 2.3,
        "text": "Now let's break these words down."
      },
      {
        "start": 60.1,
        "duration": 3.1,
        "text": "Express, you may recognize the prefix ex,"
      },
      {
        "start": 63.3,
        "duration": 2.4,
        "text": "which means out or from,"
      },
      {
        "start": 65.7,
        "duration": 2.3,
        "text": "and then of course there's press."
      },
      {
        "start": 68.0,
        "duration": 1.2,
        "text": "It's got Latin origins, sure,"
      },
      {
        "start": 69.2,
        "duration": 1.6,
        "text": "but it's an English word all its own."
      },
      {
        "start": 70.9,
        "duration": 1.0,
        "text": "It means press."
      },
      {
        "start": 71.8,
        "duration": 4.5,
        "text": "So express means to\npress out, to squish out."
      },
      {
        "start": 76.3,
        "duration": 2.1,
        "text": "Say I take a whole bunch of olives"
      },
      {
        "start": 78.5,
        "duration": 1.7,
        "text": "and I put 'em in a press"
      },
      {
        "start": 80.2,
        "duration": 1.8,
        "text": "and I squeeze them really hard."
      },
      {
        "start": 82.0,
        "duration": 2.3,
        "text": "They're going to express some olive oil."
      },
      {
        "start": 84.3,
        "duration": 3.1,
        "text": "I'm going to press the oil out of them."
      },
      {
        "start": 87.5,
        "duration": 2.4,
        "text": "And what if we switch around the prefixes"
